      <section eId="sec_13_4_6">
        <num>13-4.6</num>
        <heading>Effect of registration in beneficiary form</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_13_4_6__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The designation of a TOD beneficiary on a registration in\nbeneficiary form has no effect on ownership until the owner's death. A\nregistration of a security in beneficiary form may be canceled or\nchanged at any time by the sole owner or all then surviving owners\nwithout the consent of the beneficiary.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_13_4_6__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A registration in beneficiary form can be revoked or amended by an\nexpress direction in the owner's will which specifically refers to such\nregistration.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
